unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?][? if genaro_canje = 1 : The canje was done once. The state does not intend to be embarrassed twice. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; genaro_canje = 1; organizers += 1; members += 1; represion += 4; expediente += 5; guerrilla_meter += 2; sup_students += 2

It is his signature and he performs it like a thesis: a cacique lifted from his own fiesta, held courteously, and priced not in money but in people — named prisoners, flown where the state must watch them land free. Among the names on the list, quietly, two of yours: an organizer taken in the spring, a courier nobody expected to see again. The Party denounces kidnapping in a communiqué of impeccable orthodoxy, and the two who landed free are working again within the month. Guerrero understands the transaction perfectly. So does Bucareli, which is the expensive part.
